    <hr>
    <h4>Welcome
        <hr>
    </h4>
    <p>Many a times people aren't aware of the crop prices in different Mandi across India. So we bring you the current
        crop price present at different places in India</p>

    <p>Just select the state then district and then desired Mandi across India and get the information.</p>
    <div class="card">
        <h5 class="card-header">Graph</h5>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Check Crop prices in India !!</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Just Click on Query to see</p>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" id="myBtn">
                Query
            </button>
        </div>
        <div id="query_item"></div><br>
        <div id="chart">
            <canvas id="myChart"></canvas>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="myModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">&times;</span>
            <form>
                <div class="form-column w-75 p-3">
                    <div class="col">
                        <label>State</label>
                        <select id='list_state' class="custom-select" id="inputGroupSelect01">
                            <option></option>
                        </select>
                    </div><br>
                    <div class="col">
                        <label>District</label>
                        <select id='list_district' class="custom-select" id="inputGroupSelect01">
                            <option></option>
                        </select>
                    </div><br>
                    <div class="col">
                        <label>Market</label>
                        <select id='list_market' class="custom-select" id="inputGroupSelect01">
                            <option></option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div><br>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
